{{refimprove|date=July 2012}} {{Infobox official post |post = {{nowrap|Secretary of Science and Technology}} |native_name = ''Kalihim ng Agham at Teknolohiya'' |body = |insignia = DOST seal.svg |insigniasize = 120px |insigniacaption = Logo of the DOST |image = Fortunato dela Pena (05010376) (45364247344) (cropped).jpg |imagesize = |incumbent = [[Fortunato de la Peña]] |incumbentsince = June 30, 2016 |style = |appointer = The [[President of the Philippines|President]] with the consent of the [[Commission on Appointments]] |appointerpost = |termlength = No fixed term |formation = January 30, 1987 |inaugural = Antonio V. Arizabal |website = {{URL|www.dost.gov.ph}} }} The '''Secretary of Science and Technology''' ([[Filipino language|Filipino]]: ''Kalihim ng Agham at Teknolohiya'') is the head of the [[Department of Science and Technology (Philippines)|Department of Science and Technology]] and is a member of the [[Cabinet of the Philippines|President’s Cabinet]].
The position was created in 1987 by the then president [[Corazon Aquino]], and was first assumed by Antonio Arizabal.
The current Secretary is [[Fortunato de la Peña]], who assumed office on June 30, 2016.
